Package: nepalidate
Type: Package
Title: Convert Between Bikram Sambat (BS) and Anno Domini (AD) Dates
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Sabin", "Subedi", , "contact@sabinsubedi.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Provides functions to convert dates between the Nepali Bikram Sambat (BS) 
    calendar and the Gregorian (AD) calendar. The package supports BS years from 1970 
    to 2099 and includes validation for date ranges and formats. Functions are vectorized
    to work seamlessly with data frames and vectors.
